%% Data Flow Diagram - Text Generation Inference Server (TGIS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as KServe/ModelMesh Client
    participant Router as Router (Rust)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (optional)
    participant Batcher as Batcher/Queue<br/>(in-process)
    participant Shard0 as Model Shard 0<br/>UDS gRPC<br/>GPU 0
    participant ShardN as Model Shard N<br/>UDS gRPC<br/>GPU N
    participant GPU as CUDA/NVLink

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: Text Generation Request (gRPC)

    Client->>Router: gRPC Generate/GenerateStream<br/>8033/TCP, TLS (optional), mTLS (optional)
    Router->>Router: Validate request + Tokenize input<br/>(HuggingFace Tokenizers)
    Router->>Batcher: Queue request for batching
    Batcher->>Shard0: gRPC over UDS<br/>/tmp/text-generation-server-0<br/>plaintext
    Batcher->>ShardN: gRPC over UDS<br/>/tmp/text-generation-server-N<br/>plaintext

    Shard0->>GPU: CUDA inference<br/>PCIe/NVLink
    ShardN->>GPU: CUDA inference<br/>PCIe/NVLink

    Note over Shard0,ShardN: NCCL AllReduce (29500/TCP)<br/>Tensor Parallel Synchronization

    Shard0-->>Shard0: Aggregate results
    GPU-->>Shard0: Inference result
    Shard0-->>Batcher: gRPC response over UDS
    Batcher-->>Router: Decoded tokens
    Router-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>8033/TCP, TLS (optional)

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: Health Check

    participant Kubelet as Kubelet

    Kubelet->>Router: GET /health<br/>3000/TCP HTTP plaintext
    Router->>Shard0: Health check<br/>gRPC over UDS, plaintext
    Shard0-->>Router: Health status
    Router-->>Kubelet: HTTP 200 OK<br/>3000/TCP plaintext

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 3: Metrics Scrape

    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Prom->>Router: GET /metrics<br/>3000/TCP HTTP plaintext
    Router-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>3000/TCP plaintext
